<table width="100%" border="0" cellpadding="4"><tr bgcolor="#000000"><td><font color="#FFFFFF"><font face="Haettenschweiler, Tahoma, Arial" size="6">Extraordinary Resilience/The Enduring Evil</font></td></tr></table><table width="100%" border="0" cellpadding="4" cellspacing="0"><tr><td></td><td>&nbsp;</td></tr><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font face="Haettenschweiler, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif" size="5" COLOR="#000000">Author</Font></TD><TD><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Kefka</FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font face="Haettenschweiler, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif" size="5" COLOR="#000000">Description</Font></TD><TD><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Stealthy hobbits sneak by and absorb wounds like sponges. Sauron corrupts, enduring evil slaughters.</FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font face="Haettenschweiler, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif" size="5" COLOR="#000000">Cards</Font></TD><TD><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Starting:<br>
<br>
<!--182-->The One Ring, The Ruling Ring<br>
<!--173-->Frodo, Old Bilbo&#39;s Heir<br>
<!--193-->Sam, Son of Hamfast<br>
<!--188-->Pippin, Friend to Frodo<br>
<!--874-->Merry, Friend to Sam<br>
<br>
Adventure Deck:<br>
<br>
