[5] <!--228-->The Bridge of Khazad-dum<br>
[6] Valley of the Silverlode<br>
[7] <!--233-->Anduin Wilderland<br>
[8] <!--238-->Shores of Nen Hithoel<br>
[9] <!--242-->Summit of Amon Hen<br>
<br>
